This product downloads and uses third-party model weights at runtime. The
weights are NOT bundled in this repository or in the AppImages; they are fetched
on first use into the per-user cache directory.

================================================================================
Segment Anything (SAM) and SAM 2 / SAM 2.1
================================================================================
Object segmentation uses ONNX exports of Meta AI's Segment Anything models.

  - SAM 2.1 (Hiera tiny / small / base_plus / large)
    Copyright (c) Meta Platforms, Inc. and affiliates.
    Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
    https://github.com/facebookresearch/sam2
    ONNX weights: https://huggingface.co/vietanhdev/segment-anything-2.1-onnx-models

  - MobileSAM (the low-VRAM / CPU rung)
    Copyright (c) 2023 Chaoning Zhang and contributors.
    Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
    https://github.com/ChaoningZhang/MobileSAM
    ONNX weights: https://huggingface.co/Acly/MobileSAM

A copy of the Apache License 2.0 is available at:
  https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

