Background removal (rembg / BiRefNet / U^2-Net / IS-Net)
================================================================================
Background removal is provided by rembg (MIT) and the ONNX models it downloads
(BiRefNet, IS-Net, U^2-Net, Silueta), each under their respective licenses.
  https://github.com/danielgatis/rembg

